narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: The room was a little small for the size of the class and plagued by poor temperature control (either very hot or very cold). It was nice have a place outside the our typical building, but not worth the discomfort.
Books in the library were there - some weren't but I managed.
